<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=8272&amp;p=35383#p35383"><![CDATA[
I stretched the search box at each end to match the first column, <br />and put a minuscule bit of color on jump view.<br /><br />Edit: I now think I will have to add another option to have menu brighter, and brighter, until it's atomic bright, with black text, <br />so it's like on the &quot;Metro Variations&quot;, but have it as glass, not Metro color text.<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Edit: I removed revB, and put the final renamed skin here.<br />Now it's called &quot;Opaque Light White Split&quot;, <br />because it now has one frill option to boost menu glass brightness.<br />I passed up making the atomic brightness, <br />as well, I removed the small amount of glass color on jump view, <br />as depending on what color was showing, it would either be too much color, <br />or not enough. It's stuck on one grey blue color now.<br /><br />Done<br /><br />EDIT: Updated picture<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=856">juniper7</a> — Mon Feb 05, 2018 8:10 am</p><hr />
